Drawn against the home nation, Rene Plant's team won their encounter 2-1 on Monday, with wins for Katie Poluta in the singles and then a doubles triumph for the team of Madrie le Roux and Chanel Simmonds. The South Africans are drawn in Pool A along with Montenegro, Finland and Kenya. In the other result from their pool, Finland easily defeated Kenya, 3-0. Results: Finland beat Kenya 3-0 South Africa beat Montenegro 2-1 Singles Katie Poluta (RSA) bt Anja Draskovic (MNE) 6-2, 4-6, 6-2 Chanel Simmonds (RSA) lost to Danka Kovinic (MNE) 4-6, 5-7 Doubles Madrie le Roux/Chanel Simmonds (RSA) bt Anja Draskovic/Danka Kovinic (MNE) 6-2, 6-1 --News24--